      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Comparing要分三种情况：APY差异小于0.5%走NoAction，等于0.5%但变化小于50%走SmallRebalance，等于50%走LargeRebalance。这是关键的风控逻辑。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Comparing",
        "NoAction",
        "SmallRebalance",
        "LargeRebalance",
