    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把这三条分支画出来了。NoAction直接emit RebalanceSkipped回到Idle。SmallRebalance触发Callback给Broker然后进入Executing。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NoAction",
